_sText:
Hello Guys,

I made a new map called bhop_simpleblue
Like it says in the name I tried to keep itas simple as  possible.
If you find some bugs you can always report the bug in the comment section.
About the Map:
  • This map has 4 stages.
  • Difficulty of this map is Tier 1
  • You could run this map in under 20 seconds
  • I made this map in 3 days.
 You can send me  your speedruns of the map on my Steam Profile and im going to put them in the  description.

Have Fun playing it!
